Time Complexity: O(n²) because string concatenation creates new strings repeatedly.



#3rd approach

left=0
chars=list(s)
right=len(chars)-1
while left<right :
    chars[left], chars[right]= chars[right], chars[left]
    left+=1
    right-=1
print("".join(chars))
Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(n)



